display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {C}]]></fr:tex> is stable under direct factors, direct sums, and tensor products;
        the Tate constant families <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {Q}(n)]]></fr:tex> (for <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n\in \mathbb {Z}]]></fr:tex>) are in <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {C}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree>

    <fr:tree
