display="inline"><![CDATA[H\in \operatorname {Ob}\mathcal {C}]]></fr:tex>, there exists a local system <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[H'_\mathbb {Z}]]></fr:tex> on <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex> of free <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {Z}]]></fr:tex>-modules such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[H'_\mathbb {Z}\otimes \mathbb {Q}\approx  H_\mathbb {Q}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree>

